   ADV \& TRUSTED COMP/IEEE 15TH INT CONF SCALABLE COMP \& COMMUN/IEEE INT
   CONF CLOUD \& BIG DATA COMP/IEEE INT CONF INTERNET PEOPLE AND ASSOCIATED
   SYMPOSIA/WORKSHOPS},
Year = {2015},
Pages = {512-516},
Note = {12th IEEE Int Conf Ubiquitous Intelligence \& Comp/12th IEEE Int Conf
   Autonom \& Trusted Comp/15th IEEE Int Conf Scalable Comp \& Commun \&
   Associated Workshops/IEEE Int Conf Cloud \& Big Data Comp/IEEE Int Conf
   Internet People, Beijing, PEOPLES R CHINA, AUG 10-14, 2015},
