Abstract = {The article briefly expresses the possibilities of creating a cybernetic
   space model of the current Internet environment as a classic means of
   committing cyber crime as well as detecting these forms of crime. Part
   of the paper deals with the basic principles of the use of artificial
   intelligence to identify (identify) the basic and possible virtual
   images of criminalistic versions, primary and even urgent acts at the
