Volume = {258},
Pages = {171-175},
Note = {15th Annual Workshop on E-Business (WEB), Fort Worth, TX, DEC 12, 2015},
Abstract = {Video surveillance has become the main tool due to its rich, intuitive
   and accurate information. However, with the large-scale construction of
   video surveillance systems all over the world, problems such as ``useful
   information and clues cannot be found immediately with video big
   data{''} decrease detecting efficiency during crime prediction and
   public security governance. This paper concludes a novel architecture
   for next generation public security system, and the ``front+back{''}
   pattern is adopted. Under the architecture, cloud computing technologies
   such as distributed storage and computing, data retrieval of huge and
   heterogeneous data are introduced, and multiple optimized strategies to
   enhance the utilization of resources and efficiency of tasks.},
