   Student Chapter},
Abstract = {Analysis of crime is essential for providing safety and security to the
   civilian population. Using data mining, we can discover critical
   information which can help local authorities detect crime and areas of
   importance. The main purpose of this paper is to analyze the crime which
   entails theft, homicide and various drug offences which also include
   suspicious activities, noise complaints and burglar alarm by using
   qualitative and quantitative approach. Using K-means clustering data
   mining approach on a crime dataset from New South Wales region of
   Australia, crime rates of each type of crimes and cities with high crime
   rates have been found.},
