   Forum; 5G Based Smart Factory Standardizat Forum; Jeju Convent \&
   Visitors Bur; Korea Assoc Photon Ind Dev},
Abstract = {In this paper, the machine learning-based estimation technique of crime
   types and crime risk score is introduced. For development of the
   estimation technique, the system platform of the introduced technique is
   also implemented. To predict the crime risk score, crime risk score
   equation is designed based on the crime severity and degree of damage,
   and numerical crime risk score is applied to each criminal case. For the
   crime types and crime risk score estimation, virtual police security
   data is considered. The data form is the same as the KICS data form.
   Using the proposed technique and implemented system platform, police can
   obtain efficient information in the first stage of criminal case
   reception.},
